---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="The Best Business English Tutors for 2026" description="Advance your career by mastering the English you need for meetings, presentations, and negotiations.">
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-emerald-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Guide</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">The Best Business English Tutors for 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">Advance your career by mastering the English you need for meetings, presentations, and negotiations.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
    <p class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Why Business English?</p>
    <p class="text-emerald-800">General English focuses on social situations. Business English focuses on outcomes. It is the difference between "How are you?" and "Let's discuss the quarterly projections."</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">1. Preply Business</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Preply has built a dedicated platform for corporate language training. They offer customized dashboards for companies to track employee progress. For individual learners, their search filters allow you to find tutors who have worked in specific industries like Finance, Tech, or Law.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">2. British Council (English Online)</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">The British Council offers highly structured group and private lessons. Their "Business and Professional" track is world-renowned. It is more expensive than marketplace options, but the curriculum is incredibly polished and recognized by employers worldwide.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">3. italki (Executive Coaching)</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">On italki, you can find executive coaches who specialize in high-level business English. These are often former business professionals themselves. They provide the most flexible and personalized coaching for specific needs like preparing for a keynote speech.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-16 mb-6">Comparison Table</h2>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto">
    <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse border border-gray-200">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-gray-50">
          <th class="p-4 border">Platform</th>
          <th class="p-4 border">Best For</th>
          <th class="p-4 border">Avg. Price</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="p-4 border font-bold">Preply</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">Industry-specific tutors</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">$20 - $45/hr</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="p-4 border font-bold">British Council</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">Structured curriculum</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">$15/lesson (group)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="p-4 border font-bold">italki</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">1-on-1 executive coaching</td>
          <td class="p-4 border">$25 - $60/hr</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-emerald-600 rounded-2xl text-white">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Take the next step in your career</h3>
    <p class="mb-6">Don't let a language barrier hold you back from your next promotion. Find your business English tutor today.</p>
    <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="bg-white text-emerald-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-block">See Business Tutors</a>
  </div>
</article>
</Base>
